com.heaven7.java.reflectyio

接口 Commissioner


  • public interface Commissioner
    indicate the member is a commissioner. it can write and read data self. this often extend MemberProxy.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.0.1

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void read(com.heaven7.java.reflecty.iota.TypeAdapter<ReflectyWriter,ReflectyReader> adapter, java.lang.Object obj, ReflectyReader source)
      read the data self. often you should use MemberProxy.setValue(Object, Object) to set the read value.
      void write(com.heaven7.java.reflecty.iota.TypeAdapter<ReflectyWriter,ReflectyReader> adapter, ReflectyWriter sink, java.lang.Object value)
      write the data to the sink as Commissioner like.
